    "summary": "Renowned professional in International Film & Television Sales and film-distribution with over 25 years of international rights licensing and film-distribution experience in; Theatrical and television  drama series..\nThe Dutch Features sales agency was founded in 2012 and has grown into one of European leading Agency for mainstream Box-office hits  such as successful  family-films, thrillers and top notch drama-series such as The Godless.\nIn 2012 Dutch Features kicked off with a succes for Dutch TV-Drama and secured  a worldwide distribution deal with Content Media Corporation for Dutch produced miniseries: \"Freddy\" ( Heineken) Starring Thom Hoffman.\n\nVan Collem additionally initiated and co-produced the Internationally succesful and highly awarded Film: \u201cBuddha\u201ds Lost Children\u201d in 2006 in Thailand. \nThe film has become one of the most succesful Dutch non-fiction festival-films, with more then 10 International awards and over 60.000 cinematickets sold at the Dutch boxoffice.The Film was selected as the official Dutch entry to the Academy Awards 2008, category; Best Feature Documentary.\n\nWebsites: www.dutchfeatures.com\n                \n                \n\nFor more information contact : \npim@dutchfeatures.com\nT: 31-(0)-647125430\n\nSpecialties: Initiated and succesfully managed several major Film and TV distribution company's, such as;  Polygram Televison Benelux, ( Now Vivendi Unversal)) and worldwide distributor; Endemol International Distribution as MD.\n\nCo-developed and co-financed several features and non-fiction films such as one of Holland's highly awarded film documentaries: \"Buddha's lost Children\".",
